    "In addition, the RF::Morgan models proposed herein have comparable or superior performance to the models of Merget et al., i.e.",
    "it exhibited average AUC value of 0.774 on 354 kinases and achieved HQ models on 259 kinases.The results illustrated that the comprehensive kinase profiling dataset with large structural diversity and chemical space constructed in this paper is necessary for building robust and reliable kinase profiling prediction models, as well as the optimal combination of ML algorithms and molecular feature representations can help to develop more accurate models for the virtual profiling prediction of kinase inhibitors.",
